      • Serialisierte Felder

        • ELEMENT_INDEX
          byte ELEMENT_INDEX
          The atomic number of the element displayed in this window. This is used to identify the element and retrieve its properties. It is a byte value, as atomic numbers are typically small integers.
        • TRUE_DIMENSION
          Dimension TRUE_DIMENSION
          The true dimension of the JFrame, which is used to reset the window size to its original dimensions when needed. This is set when the window is initialized and can be retrieved later.
